{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitNext\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Action</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitNext</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stopAtFirstFailure </span><span class=\"fn\">compress</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action\">Action</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Selects a case-split from the list of candidates, performs the split and applies\ncontinuation to all subgoals.\nIf a subgoal is solved without using new hypotheses, closes the original goal using this proof. That is,\nit performs non-chronological backtracking.\n\nIf `stopsAtFirstFailure = true`, it stops the search as soon as the given continuation cannot solve a subgoal.\n\nIf `compress = true`, then it uses `<;>` to generate the resulting tactic sequence if all subgoal sequences are\nidentical. For example, suppose that the following sequence is generated with `compress = false`\n```\ncases #50fc\nnext => lia\nnext => lia\n```\nThen with `compress = true` it generates `cases #50fc <;> lia`\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitNext","kind":"def","line":534,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitNext","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L534-L565"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitCore\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Action</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitInfo\">SplitInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">numCases</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">isRec </span><span class=\"fn\">stopAtFirstFailure </span><span class=\"fn\">compress</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">candidates?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitInfo\">SplitInfo</a>)</span></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action\">Action</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Performs a case-split using `c`.\nRemark: `numCases` and `isRec` are computed using `checkSplitStatus`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitCore","kind":"def","line":446,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.splitCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L446-L532"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.isSorryAlt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Action</span>.<span class=\"name\">isSorryAlt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">alt</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`grind</span>)</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.isSorryAlt","kind":"def","line":418,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Action.isSorryAlt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L418-L423"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.toSyntax\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">toSyntax</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">info</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax\">TSyntax</a> <span class=\"fn\">`grind</span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates the anchor reference syntax for the result of `mkSplitAnchorRefInfo`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.toSyntax","kind":"def","line":340,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.toSyntax","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L340-L348"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkSplitAnchorRefInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSplitAnchorRefInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitInfo\">SplitInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">candidates?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitInfo\">SplitInfo</a>)</span></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Computes the anchor reference information for the case-split candidate `c`.\nThe candidate list must be the one stored in the goal before the case-split is selected and\nperformed (i.e., before `selectNextSplit?` prunes the list and before `c` is marked as resolved),\nso that it matches the list inspected by the `cases` tactic when replaying the generated script.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkSplitAnchorRefInfo","kind":"def","line":321,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkSplitAnchorRefInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L321-L338"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.ordinal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">ordinal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.ordinal","kind":"def","line":319,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.ordinal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L319-L319"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.anchor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">anchor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt64\">UInt64</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.anchor","kind":"def","line":318,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.anchor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L318-L318"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.numDigits\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">numDigits</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.numDigits","kind":"def","line":317,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.numDigits","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L317-L317"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt64\">UInt64</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\">Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo</a></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.mk","kind":"ctor","line":309,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L309-L319"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitAnchorRefInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Anchor reference for a case-split candidate in generated tactic scripts.\n`ordinal` is the 0-based position of the candidate among the (ready) candidates whose\nanchors share the same displayed prefix. Distinct candidates may have identical anchors\n(e.g., candidates that differ only in inaccessible variables), and the ordinal is used\nto disambiguate them.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo","kind":"structure","line":309,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitAnchorRefInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L309-L319"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getSplitCandidateAnchors\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">getSplitCandidateAnchors</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">filter</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span> := <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">candidates?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitInfo\">SplitInfo</a>)</span></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors\">SplitCandidateAnchors</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns case-split candidates. Case-splits that are tagged as `.resolved` or `.notReady` are skipped.\nApplies additional `filter` if provided.\nIf `candidates?` is provided, it is used instead of the candidates stored in the goal.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getSplitCandidateAnchors","kind":"def","line":281,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.getSplitCandidateAnchors","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L281-L307"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors.numDigits\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitCandidateAnchors</span>.<span class=\"name\">numDigits</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors\">SplitCandidateAnchors</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Number of digits (≥ 4) sufficient for distinguishing anchors. We usually display only the first `numDigits`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors.numDigits","kind":"def","line":279,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors.numDigits","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.lean#L279-L279"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors.candidates\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">SplitCandidateAnchors</span>.<span class=\"name\">candidates</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors\">SplitCandidateAnchors</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateWithAnchor\">SplitCandidateWithAnchor</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Pairs `(anchor, split)` ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Split.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.SplitCandidateAnchors.candidates","kind":"def","line":277,"name":"Lean.Meta